data.description: 14 Millard Circle is a lovely 4BR/2 1/5 Bath Raised Ranch, with brick fireplace, large kitchen, and beautiful natural light.  Main level features primary bedroom, ensuite bath, two additional bedrooms and a renovated full bath.  The lower level has a family room, another bedroom which can easily be used as an office or guest room, and a half bath.  The property boasts a huge backyard with a 27' above-ground pool and a two-level deck.  The attached garage has room for two cars.  Monroe Village is 45 minutes from NYC and near the Woodbury Commons outlet center.
